  ('bookkeeper-moex-00785', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-108-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '外國之事業、機關、團體、組織在中華民國境內無固定營業場所，銷售電子勞務予境內自然人者，下列 何者為營業稅之納稅義務人？', '["無須繳納營業稅", "外國之事業、機關、團體、組織", "電子勞務之買受人", "營業人或買受人協調擇一繳納"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "649483717ea0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e003a99a2c64", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108180", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00786', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-108-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '為防止逃漏、控制稅源及促進統一發票之推行，財政部得訂定統一發票給獎辦法；其經費由全年營業稅 收入總額中提出百分之多少以資支應？', '["百分之一", "百分之二", "百分之三", "百分之五"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "649483717ea0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e003a99a2c64", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108180", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00787', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-108-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者適用之營業稅法定稅率最低？', '["一般小規模營業人", "農產品批發市場之承銷人", "保險業之再保費收入", "國際運輸用之船舶、航空器及遠洋漁船"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "649483717ea0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e003a99a2c64", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108180", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
